1
00:00:00,470 --> 00:00:01,910
(All people, incidents,
and backgrounds...)

2
00:00:01,910 --> 00:00:03,380
(in this drama are fictitious
and unrelated to reality.)

3
00:00:03,380 --> 00:00:04,810
(Also, children were filmed
under production guidelines.)

4
00:00:06,580 --> 00:00:07,580
My gosh.

5
00:00:08,210 --> 00:00:10,280
- Gosh, he's hurting me.
- Mom.

6
00:00:10,580 --> 00:00:11,620
Why you...

7
00:00:11,920 --> 00:00:12,950
Baek Jin Ju?

8
00:00:13,690 --> 00:00:14,690
What?

9
00:00:15,250 --> 00:00:17,820
Choi Yu Na, what is she saying?

10
00:00:18,960 --> 00:00:20,660
Well...

11
00:00:22,490 --> 00:00:23,500
My gosh.

12
00:00:23,960 --> 00:00:26,600
Baek Jin Ju is alive. Chloe...

13
00:00:28,530 --> 00:00:29,930
Chloe was Baek Jin Ju all along.

14
00:00:50,760 --> 00:00:52,190
You said Baek Jin Ju was dead.

15
00:00:53,490 --> 00:00:55,760
You said you were sure of it.

16
00:00:57,330 --> 00:00:59,130
I don't know how this happened.

17
00:00:59,560 --> 00:01:02,670
Seven years ago,
she was definitely dead.

18
00:01:02,800 --> 00:01:05,570
You have the nerve to use that
as an excuse?

19
00:01:06,570 --> 00:01:07,570
Now,

20
00:01:09,340 --> 00:01:11,680
who else knows this?

21
00:01:13,040 --> 00:01:14,050
Well...

22
00:01:14,580 --> 00:01:16,710
Kim Dan Hui and Park Min Jun.

23
00:01:17,920 --> 00:01:20,590
They seem to know too.
Is that right?

24
00:01:21,590 --> 00:01:24,960
Who else knows? Tell me everything!

25
00:01:25,520 --> 00:01:28,660
That's right.
I think Park Min Jun knows.

26
00:01:29,530 --> 00:01:31,160
And as for Hyun Jun...

27
00:01:32,600 --> 00:01:33,900
He doesn't know.

28
00:01:36,000 --> 00:01:37,000
You.

29
00:01:37,070 --> 00:01:40,810
Lay low and don't make a move.

30
00:01:41,170 --> 00:01:44,810
I'll take care of Baek Jin Ju first.
You're next.

31
00:01:45,710 --> 00:01:47,450
Take care of me?

32
00:01:49,050 --> 00:01:51,550
Sir, I'll do anything.

33
00:01:51,680 --> 00:01:53,720
Please give me a chance
to make things right.

34
00:01:53,720 --> 00:01:54,750
Quiet!

35
00:01:55,720 --> 00:01:59,460
If you don't want to die right here,
get out now.

36
00:02:11,370 --> 00:02:13,200
Let go of me!

37
00:02:13,200 --> 00:02:16,140
Can't you hear
all that screaming in there?

38
00:02:16,170 --> 00:02:19,110
Before he eats Yu Na alive,
I have to go in.

39
00:02:19,680 --> 00:02:23,210
For goodness' sake.
Are you kidding me?

40
00:02:23,280 --> 00:02:25,820
Oh, no. Yu Na!

41
00:02:26,720 --> 00:02:28,720
What's all this noise?

42
00:02:41,400 --> 00:02:43,640
What is it? What on earth happened?

43
00:02:49,770 --> 00:02:52,110
You witch!

44
00:03:01,290 --> 00:03:05,460
People are wondering
why I chose Adele Group.

45
00:03:05,520 --> 00:03:09,690
But I'm wondering
why the Adele Group...

46
00:03:10,230 --> 00:03:11,530
chose Temi Bio.

47
00:03:12,060 --> 00:03:14,500
So back then, she deliberately...

48
00:03:14,970 --> 00:03:18,140
brought a film crew to ask me that.

49
00:03:19,670 --> 00:03:22,710
She wanted to know...

50
00:03:23,170 --> 00:03:24,680
the reason Baek Jun Gi died.

51
00:03:32,120 --> 00:03:35,020
I knew it.
You didn't lose your memory.

52
00:03:35,090 --> 00:03:37,920
You actually faked amnesia
just to team up with Kim Dan Hui...

53
00:03:38,620 --> 00:03:40,790
and stab me in the back.

54
00:03:41,260 --> 00:03:42,290
Yes.

55
00:03:42,890 --> 00:03:44,100
That's right.

56
00:03:44,900 --> 00:03:49,000
I haven't forgotten
what happened at the warehouse.

57
00:03:49,930 --> 00:03:51,100
Baek Jin Ju.

58
00:03:52,600 --> 00:03:57,540
You've been deceiving me
with lies from the start?

59
00:03:59,040 --> 00:04:01,510
You just had to join forces
with Kim Dan Hui...

60
00:04:01,580 --> 00:04:04,880
and drag up everything
that happened 30 years ago.

61
00:04:04,950 --> 00:04:08,990
Now you'll try to reveal
what happened seven years ago too.

62
00:04:10,360 --> 00:04:15,190
And Kim Dan Hui will no doubt
help Baek Jin Ju.

63
00:04:19,600 --> 00:04:22,670
Kim Dan Hui. Baek Jin Ju.

64
00:04:26,270 --> 00:04:29,970
I have to break them apart first.

65
00:04:34,680 --> 00:04:35,680
What?

66
00:04:36,580 --> 00:04:38,450
Temi Bio? Chloe?

67
00:04:40,120 --> 00:04:43,690
Chloe is Baek Jin Ju,
the daughter of Temi Bio's CEO?

68
00:04:44,060 --> 00:04:46,990
And she's alive and well
and married to Hyun Jun?

69
00:04:47,790 --> 00:04:49,730
Yes, that's right.

70
00:04:54,430 --> 00:04:57,670
What about our Hyun Jun?
Does he know or not?

71
00:04:58,270 --> 00:04:59,400
Park Hyun Jun...

72
00:05:01,940 --> 00:05:03,440
He shouldn't have known, right?

73
00:05:03,910 --> 00:05:07,210
Even when the chairman asked me,
I told him Hyun Jun didn't know.

74
00:05:08,110 --> 00:05:09,110
You did?

75
00:05:10,920 --> 00:05:13,720
I was covering for him.

76
00:05:14,050 --> 00:05:17,260
Since I'm keeping
two of his secrets,

77
00:05:17,490 --> 00:05:19,160
from now on, you have to help me.

78
00:05:19,490 --> 00:05:22,590
I need you to stop the chairman
from coming after me.

79
00:05:23,960 --> 00:05:26,330
It's obvious you messed up the job
Park Tae Ho gave you,

80
00:05:26,330 --> 00:05:28,200
and now you're cornered.

81
00:05:28,900 --> 00:05:31,040
For now, you'd better figure out
how to save yourself.

82
00:05:31,040 --> 00:05:33,040
My only concern at the moment
is my Hyun Jun.

83
00:05:33,370 --> 00:05:34,710
Let go of me.

84
00:05:47,920 --> 00:05:50,460
I heard you went
to Ms. Choi's house.

85
00:05:51,090 --> 00:05:53,660
I thought you'd be feeling down,
so I asked you to come over.

86
00:05:54,690 --> 00:05:55,760
Right.

87
00:05:56,760 --> 00:06:00,360
I let out seven years
of resentment,

88
00:06:01,530 --> 00:06:03,230
but instead of feeling relieved,

89
00:06:03,470 --> 00:06:05,670
it just broke my heart
thinking of my dad.

90
00:06:05,670 --> 00:06:06,670
Of course.

91
00:06:08,010 --> 00:06:09,410
I've been there too.

92
00:06:10,110 --> 00:06:11,410
I know exactly how you feel.

93
00:06:13,480 --> 00:06:17,420
You two talk.
We're going to the grocery store.

94
00:06:17,620 --> 00:06:19,580
Jin Ju, you should stay for dinner.

95
00:06:20,250 --> 00:06:21,690
You really should.

96
00:06:21,690 --> 00:06:24,360
It's better to be around people
on a day like today.

97
00:06:24,620 --> 00:06:25,960
Let's have dinner together.

98
00:06:26,490 --> 00:06:28,330
- We won't take long.
- Okay.

99
00:06:28,390 --> 00:06:29,390
- See you later.
- Sure.

100
00:06:31,530 --> 00:06:32,530
Have a seat.

101
00:06:38,370 --> 00:06:41,710
Jin Ju, there's something
I need to tell you.

102
00:06:42,210 --> 00:06:44,880
Oh Jung Ran came by
a little while ago.

103
00:06:45,440 --> 00:06:47,780
Oh Jung Ran? Why all of a sudden?

104
00:06:47,880 --> 00:06:50,780
She needs to make Hyun Jun
the next chairman,

105
00:06:51,180 --> 00:06:52,220
but I know...

106
00:06:53,020 --> 00:06:55,150
a secret about Hyun Jun.

107
00:06:57,220 --> 00:07:00,420
That he isn't Park Tae Ho's son?

108
00:07:00,860 --> 00:07:03,860
- You knew too?
- Yes.

109
00:07:04,600 --> 00:07:05,930
I knew.

110
00:07:07,000 --> 00:07:11,240
You must've wanted to protect
his secret, just like Min Jun did.

111
00:07:11,440 --> 00:07:12,440
That's right.

112
00:07:12,440 --> 00:07:15,570
I assume Oh Jung Ran asked you
to keep his secret.

113
00:07:16,140 --> 00:07:19,010
She did.
So I gave her my conditions.

114
00:07:19,810 --> 00:07:21,550
In exchange for keeping his secret,

115
00:07:22,080 --> 00:07:24,720
she has to bring me
Park Tae Ho's slush fund ledger.

116
00:07:24,920 --> 00:07:27,920
Are you trading the chairmanship
for the slush fund ledger?

117
00:07:27,990 --> 00:07:30,720
It doesn't mean we're giving up
on the chairmanship.

118
00:07:31,920 --> 00:07:33,090
It just means...

119
00:07:33,090 --> 00:07:35,690
I won't use Hyun Jun's secret
as leverage to win the seat.

120
00:07:35,860 --> 00:07:37,030
Oh Jung Ran may think...

121
00:07:37,260 --> 00:07:39,060
that as long as
Hyun Jun's secret is safe,

122
00:07:39,060 --> 00:07:41,300
he can become the chairman.

123
00:07:41,870 --> 00:07:45,970
But the race for the seat
is a whole different battle.

124
00:07:46,300 --> 00:07:48,770
In that case,
it's not a bad deal for us.

125
00:07:49,710 --> 00:07:52,940
We get the slush fund ledger
in exchange for keeping quiet,

126
00:07:53,310 --> 00:07:55,210
and we can still win
the chairmanship...

127
00:07:55,210 --> 00:07:56,480
through the competition.

128
00:08:16,800 --> 00:08:18,140
Baek Jin Ju.

129
00:08:23,570 --> 00:08:26,240
Did Choi Yu Na tell you already?

130
00:08:28,010 --> 00:08:29,010
That's right.

131
00:08:29,480 --> 00:08:33,020
I'm Baek Jin Ju.
The same Baek Jin Ju...

132
00:08:33,850 --> 00:08:35,050
you killed.

133
00:08:42,730 --> 00:08:43,730
Did you...

134
00:08:44,030 --> 00:08:46,360
know that Chloe was Baek Jin Ju?

135
00:08:47,830 --> 00:08:49,300
How did you find out?

136
00:08:50,030 --> 00:08:51,040
Don't tell me...

137
00:08:52,000 --> 00:08:55,570
Exactly. Park Tae Ho knows too,
and he's throwing a fit.

138
00:08:57,380 --> 00:08:58,380
So in the end...

139
00:08:58,980 --> 00:09:01,450
No matter what,
say you knew nothing.

140
00:09:01,850 --> 00:09:03,510
He said he'd back you
as the next chairman.

141
00:09:03,510 --> 00:09:05,250
If he finds out, you're done for.

142
00:09:06,480 --> 00:09:07,550
Don't worry.

143
00:09:08,550 --> 00:09:11,620
I was planning to say
I was used and knew nothing.

144
00:09:12,620 --> 00:09:14,890
Rather than the fact
that Father killed someone,

145
00:09:15,190 --> 00:09:17,960
I'll say the betrayal
of being used by Baek Jin Ju...

146
00:09:19,260 --> 00:09:20,770
is what hurts more.

147
00:09:22,870 --> 00:09:23,970
It's pretty much the truth.

148
00:09:25,140 --> 00:09:26,440
Hyun Jun.

149
00:09:26,570 --> 00:09:29,570
Were you hurt by the betrayal?

150
00:09:30,240 --> 00:09:34,550
You suddenly cut ties with Chloe,
the Baek Jin Ju you liked so much.

151
00:09:35,680 --> 00:09:36,880
I just figured you were mad...

152
00:09:36,880 --> 00:09:38,820
because she lied to you
and joined their side.

153
00:09:39,220 --> 00:09:40,280
You weren't just angry?

154
00:09:40,590 --> 00:09:43,020
You were actually hurt
by the betrayal?

155
00:09:44,590 --> 00:09:45,920
Stop talking about Jin Ju.

156
00:09:47,160 --> 00:09:50,030
Fine. She came charging in,
vowing revenge.

157
00:09:50,290 --> 00:09:51,560
Forget about that woman...

158
00:09:51,560 --> 00:09:53,700
and her lies about having amnesia
and being Chloe.

159
00:09:53,970 --> 00:09:55,070
No matter what,

160
00:09:55,830 --> 00:09:57,770
you stick to the story
that Baek Jin Ju used you.

161
00:09:57,940 --> 00:10:01,040
Whatever happens between
Park Tae Ho and her, stay out of it.

162
00:10:01,510 --> 00:10:02,510
Got it?

163
00:10:11,950 --> 00:10:14,050
How does someone
who was supposed to be dead...

164
00:10:14,050 --> 00:10:15,790
make it out alive,

165
00:10:17,090 --> 00:10:18,790
just to dare to stab me in the back?

166
00:10:19,360 --> 00:10:20,390
Do you really think...

167
00:10:21,090 --> 00:10:23,730
I came back from the dead
just to stab you in the back?

168
00:10:24,160 --> 00:10:26,330
You have to pay...

169
00:10:26,360 --> 00:10:28,870
for cruelly murdering my father
and framing him.

170
00:10:29,830 --> 00:10:32,440
I'll expose you
for the monster you are...

171
00:10:32,870 --> 00:10:34,810
and clear my father's name.

172
00:10:34,910 --> 00:10:35,910
I see.

173
00:10:36,670 --> 00:10:38,940
Baek Jun Gi, your father.

174
00:10:40,240 --> 00:10:42,210
He might have a right
to feel wronged.

175
00:10:44,220 --> 00:10:47,120
Park Tae Ho.
Don't lay a hand on Jin Ju.

176
00:10:49,250 --> 00:10:51,190
How touching, the two of you.

177
00:10:51,990 --> 00:10:53,120
Then again,

178
00:10:53,690 --> 00:10:55,590
now that Baek Jin Ju
has turned up alive,

179
00:10:56,160 --> 00:10:57,600
she opened the P.O. box for you.

180
00:10:57,600 --> 00:10:59,060
And on behalf of Baek Jun Gi,

181
00:11:00,060 --> 00:11:01,800
she gave you the evidence
you were looking for.

182
00:11:03,130 --> 00:11:04,700
You must be very grateful, right?

183
00:11:05,970 --> 00:11:07,910
What on earth...

184
00:11:09,110 --> 00:11:11,010
You knew about the P.O. box?

185
00:11:11,540 --> 00:11:14,410
How did you know
Dr. Baek had the evidence?

186
00:11:14,750 --> 00:11:16,710
Didn't I tell you...

187
00:11:16,780 --> 00:11:20,220
that I've always been
protecting you?

188
00:11:34,470 --> 00:11:35,500
But...

189
00:11:35,870 --> 00:11:37,540
why are you...

190
00:11:37,600 --> 00:11:40,300
I mean, how did you know I was here?

191
00:11:40,570 --> 00:11:43,640
Are you having me followed?

192
00:11:44,480 --> 00:11:45,940
It's not surveillance.

193
00:11:47,140 --> 00:11:49,450
Think of it as protection,
Myung Hui.

194
00:11:51,450 --> 00:11:53,550
Are you saying that's when...

195
00:11:54,020 --> 00:11:56,490
No matter how hard you tried,

196
00:11:57,020 --> 00:11:58,760
you were always
in the palm of my hand.

197
00:11:59,920 --> 00:12:03,930
I already knew you had arranged...

198
00:12:03,990 --> 00:12:07,400
to meet Baek Jun Gi
to get the evidence.

199
00:12:08,130 --> 00:12:11,070
That's why I made my decision.

200
00:12:11,970 --> 00:12:13,040
To have Baek Jun Gi...

201
00:12:14,570 --> 00:12:15,570
killed.

202
00:12:19,680 --> 00:12:20,680
What?

203
00:12:22,310 --> 00:12:23,310
Baek Jin Ju.

204
00:12:23,850 --> 00:12:26,080
You shouldn't be glaring at me
like that.

205
00:12:26,480 --> 00:12:28,950
I'm not the one
who killed your father.

206
00:12:29,850 --> 00:12:31,420
It was this woman, Kim Dan Hui.

207
00:12:32,190 --> 00:12:34,860
Baek Jun Gi didn't die
because I wanted Temi Bio.

208
00:12:35,730 --> 00:12:40,600
He died because Kim Dan Hui
went digging into the past.

209
00:12:42,200 --> 00:12:45,100
Kim Dan Hui. Baek Jun Gi died...

210
00:12:46,570 --> 00:12:48,340
because of you.

211
00:13:01,090 --> 00:13:03,690
No. You, Park Tae Ho,

212
00:13:04,190 --> 00:13:07,290
are the one who killed my father.

213
00:13:10,060 --> 00:13:11,960
Don't let his words get to you.

214
00:13:12,560 --> 00:13:13,600
Jin Ju.

215
00:13:15,630 --> 00:13:17,800
Are you trying to drive us apart
with those lies?

216
00:13:18,300 --> 00:13:21,840
Are you threatening to kill again
if we expose the past?

217
00:13:23,610 --> 00:13:24,910
Well, too bad.

218
00:13:25,680 --> 00:13:29,410
We share a special bond,
brought together by my father.

219
00:13:30,080 --> 00:13:33,950
Park Tae Ho.
We both lost family because of you,

220
00:13:34,220 --> 00:13:35,690
so we understand each other.

221
00:13:36,320 --> 00:13:39,160
No matter what threats you make,

222
00:13:39,820 --> 00:13:41,460
we won't be scared
into backing down.

223
00:13:43,030 --> 00:13:44,030
Shoot.

224
00:13:45,000 --> 00:13:46,000
I see.

225
00:13:46,560 --> 00:13:49,370
Baek Jin Ju, just like your father,

226
00:13:49,370 --> 00:13:52,270
it seems you plan to run wild
without fear.

227
00:13:54,000 --> 00:13:55,070
Kim Dan Hui.

228
00:13:55,670 --> 00:13:57,680
Are you just going
to stand by and watch?

229
00:13:57,980 --> 00:13:59,680
Just for your revenge,

230
00:13:59,810 --> 00:14:03,380
you're going to let
Baek Jun Gi's daughter die too?

231
00:14:03,380 --> 00:14:04,550
Shut it.

232
00:14:05,250 --> 00:14:07,890
I'm not falling
for your pathetic threats.

233
00:14:11,960 --> 00:14:14,430
- I can't believe that happened...
- It's totally fine.

234
00:14:14,830 --> 00:14:17,530
- What's going on?
- How dare you come in here?

235
00:14:17,660 --> 00:14:20,560
How dare you?
Get away from my daughter!

236
00:14:23,270 --> 00:14:24,900
You pathetic fools.

237
00:14:26,200 --> 00:14:28,740
Kim Dan Hui.
You'd better think carefully.

238
00:14:29,840 --> 00:14:34,310
If anything happens to Baek Jin Ju,
it'll all be your fault.

239
00:14:39,080 --> 00:14:40,320
Let's go.

240
00:15:03,510 --> 00:15:08,510
Hey.
Contact Detective Yun right now.

241
00:15:09,080 --> 00:15:12,920
I'm willing to pay to find out
where the police stand.

242
00:15:13,020 --> 00:15:17,490
And bring me the files on Baek Jin Ju
from seven years ago.

243
00:15:17,690 --> 00:15:19,220
Yes, sir.

244
00:15:22,360 --> 00:15:23,490
Fine.

245
00:15:25,400 --> 00:15:27,970
If they insist
on going up against me,

246
00:15:29,230 --> 00:15:31,300
then I'll have to give them
a real fight.

247
00:15:35,640 --> 00:15:36,670
Park Tae Ho...

248
00:15:38,340 --> 00:15:42,010
He knew everything on that day
seven years ago.

249
00:15:43,450 --> 00:15:45,920
While trying to help me, Dr. Baek...

250
00:15:49,150 --> 00:15:50,150
I'm so sorry.

251
00:15:51,560 --> 00:15:52,590
Because of me,

252
00:15:53,120 --> 00:15:55,530
- you and Dr. Baek...
- No.

253
00:15:56,190 --> 00:15:58,030
Don't let Park Tae Ho's words
get to you.

254
00:15:58,900 --> 00:15:59,960
He killed my father,

255
00:15:59,960 --> 00:16:01,870
and now he's trying
to turn us against each other.

256
00:16:02,070 --> 00:16:05,670
- We can't let him win.
- Exactly. Jin Ju's right.

257
00:16:06,370 --> 00:16:09,170
Park Tae Ho killed Dr. Baek
to cover up his crimes.

258
00:16:09,770 --> 00:16:12,010
We need to be even more determined
to destroy him for good.

259
00:16:12,210 --> 00:16:14,450
Okay, everyone.
Instead of doing this,

260
00:16:14,580 --> 00:16:17,410
we need to come up with a plan
to go against him.

261
00:16:18,420 --> 00:16:20,050
Now that Park Tae Ho
knows everything,

262
00:16:20,050 --> 00:16:21,950
he might target you again, Jin Ju.

263
00:16:21,950 --> 00:16:23,590
He'll try to silence you...

264
00:16:23,590 --> 00:16:26,090
because he's terrified you'll report
what happened seven years ago.

265
00:16:27,060 --> 00:16:28,060
I know.

266
00:16:30,260 --> 00:16:33,160
Seeing how shameless Park Tae Ho is,

267
00:16:33,460 --> 00:16:35,230
I can't stand it anymore.

268
00:16:36,370 --> 00:16:38,170
I filed for a provisional seizure
against Choi Yu Na...

269
00:16:38,240 --> 00:16:39,840
and got my identity back.

270
00:16:40,170 --> 00:16:42,410
The situation is different
from seven years ago,

271
00:16:42,640 --> 00:16:45,310
so I'm going to request
a reinvestigation immediately.

272
00:16:45,710 --> 00:16:47,310
Let's go to the police station
right now.

273
00:16:47,810 --> 00:16:51,350
- What? Jin Ju, wait.
- Jin Ju.

274
00:16:54,420 --> 00:16:56,620
We'll get going.

275
00:17:05,530 --> 00:17:07,430
Park Hyun Jun.

276
00:17:08,000 --> 00:17:09,000
You.

277
00:17:09,770 --> 00:17:11,140
He didn't know.

278
00:17:11,900 --> 00:17:15,070
Would he have married her
if he had known who she was?

279
00:17:15,770 --> 00:17:18,610
Yes. I only found out
after Mom called me.

280
00:17:19,510 --> 00:17:22,210
Why would she hide her identity
and marry me?

281
00:17:23,510 --> 00:17:24,780
I mean, she had Min Jun.

282
00:17:25,080 --> 00:17:27,420
She planned to use me
to take you down, didn't she?

283
00:17:28,090 --> 00:17:30,450
Because you killed CEO Baek Jun Gi.

284
00:17:31,050 --> 00:17:33,020
- Hyun Jun!
- That's right.

285
00:17:34,220 --> 00:17:35,490
Yes, I killed him.

286
00:17:36,560 --> 00:17:37,730
So what?

287
00:17:37,930 --> 00:17:39,660
If you're going
to throw a tantrum...

288
00:17:39,960 --> 00:17:42,970
and threaten to expose me
like Min Jun did, just get lost!

289
00:17:43,370 --> 00:17:46,300
No. I'm nothing like him.

290
00:17:47,400 --> 00:17:48,610
Just like you, Father,

291
00:17:49,110 --> 00:17:50,840
I was a victim
completely fooled by Baek Jin Ju.

292
00:17:51,980 --> 00:17:52,980
A victim?

293
00:17:53,340 --> 00:17:56,950
I was tricked into marrying her
and was used.

294
00:17:57,150 --> 00:17:58,720
No matter who you killed,

295
00:17:59,820 --> 00:18:01,590
the pain I feel is much greater.

296
00:18:02,090 --> 00:18:05,690
If Baek Jin Ju tries
to take you down, I'll stop her,

297
00:18:06,260 --> 00:18:07,790
and I will protect you.

298
00:18:09,290 --> 00:18:10,560
That's where I stand.

299
00:18:24,110 --> 00:18:25,310
Park Hyun Jun.

300
00:18:26,380 --> 00:18:30,080
You'd better mean
what you just said.

301
00:18:31,420 --> 00:18:33,420
- Of course.
- Right.

302
00:18:34,080 --> 00:18:37,720
All Hyun Jun cares about
is protecting the Adele Group.

303
00:18:40,520 --> 00:18:41,930
You two, follow me.

304
00:19:05,750 --> 00:19:07,680
(Park Min Jun)

305
00:19:11,090 --> 00:19:13,890
Please protect Jin Ju
from any fallout.

306
00:19:13,890 --> 00:19:15,660
If something happens to Jin Ju,

307
00:19:16,290 --> 00:19:18,030
you'll never be able
to forgive yourself.

308
00:19:18,600 --> 00:19:19,900
And neither will I.

309
00:19:20,600 --> 00:19:22,030
Call me if anything happens.

310
00:19:23,600 --> 00:19:24,600
I'm counting on you.

311
00:19:28,410 --> 00:19:29,970
(Park Min Jun)

312
00:19:30,840 --> 00:19:34,980
Park Min Jun,
protect Baek Jin Ju yourself.

313
00:19:46,990 --> 00:19:47,990
Jin Ju.

314
00:19:49,890 --> 00:19:51,400
What are you doing here?

315
00:19:51,800 --> 00:19:53,260
My mother called me.

316
00:19:53,660 --> 00:19:55,700
She said you went to request
a reinvestigation...

317
00:19:56,000 --> 00:19:57,430
and that she was worried.

318
00:19:58,970 --> 00:20:00,870
Did you file
for the reinvestigation?

319
00:20:01,340 --> 00:20:05,580
Yes. I haven't found any evidence
proving Park Tae Ho's guilt yet,

320
00:20:05,710 --> 00:20:07,610
but things are different
than they were seven years ago.

321
00:20:08,710 --> 00:20:10,680
That's right. Park Tae Ho is now...

322
00:20:11,820 --> 00:20:13,820
a murderer
known to the entire country,

323
00:20:14,450 --> 00:20:16,720
and he's no longer the chairman
of Adele Group.

324
00:20:16,790 --> 00:20:19,160
The police will decide
to reinvestigate soon.

325
00:20:19,220 --> 00:20:21,890
It'll take a few days
for them to decide, right?

326
00:20:21,890 --> 00:20:22,890
Most likely.

327
00:20:23,930 --> 00:20:25,460
You have to be very careful
until then.

328
00:20:26,130 --> 00:20:29,130
Park Tae Ho knows much more
than we think,

329
00:20:29,200 --> 00:20:31,170
and he's the kind of man
who knows how to use it.

330
00:20:32,600 --> 00:20:35,510
My mother also told me
about your father.

331
00:20:36,110 --> 00:20:38,080
My father wasn't after Temi Bio,

332
00:20:40,180 --> 00:20:41,480
but the evidence.

333
00:20:42,810 --> 00:20:45,980
My mother and I are both so sorry.

334
00:20:47,150 --> 00:20:48,750
You don't have to feel that way.

335
00:20:49,690 --> 00:20:50,820
Whatever the reason,

336
00:20:51,190 --> 00:20:53,660
Park Tae Ho is the one
who killed my dad.

337
00:20:55,430 --> 00:20:58,900
I won't be swayed or intimidated
like he wants.

338
00:21:07,600 --> 00:21:09,570
(Personal Profile: Baek Jin Ju)

339
00:21:14,180 --> 00:21:17,250
I must be crazy. I really must be.

340
00:21:17,650 --> 00:21:20,350
I'm being audited for corruption
just for getting involved with him,

341
00:21:20,920 --> 00:21:23,390
yet here I am again. Unbelievable.

342
00:21:23,590 --> 00:21:25,820
Rather than siding with the police,

343
00:21:26,320 --> 00:21:28,460
it's more profitable for you
to side with me.

344
00:21:30,460 --> 00:21:31,730
What's the word from the police?

345
00:21:33,460 --> 00:21:35,830
A petition has been filed
to reopen your investigation.

346
00:21:36,530 --> 00:21:39,970
Since it's a murder case involving
Chairman Park Tae Ho of Adele Group,

347
00:21:40,270 --> 00:21:42,910
it'll be reported directly
to the main investigation bureau.

348
00:21:43,340 --> 00:21:45,740
They'll hold a review committee...

349
00:21:46,140 --> 00:21:48,450
to decide whether or not
to reinvestigate.

350
00:21:50,480 --> 00:21:53,550
Are you sure you didn't kill
Baek Jun Gi...

351
00:21:55,090 --> 00:21:56,090
seven years ago?

352
00:22:00,490 --> 00:22:02,230
You did it. You actually did it.

353
00:22:03,160 --> 00:22:05,930
If they decide to reinvestigate,
I can't stop it.

354
00:22:06,530 --> 00:22:08,670
It's even above my pay grade
as deputy chief.

355
00:22:08,670 --> 00:22:11,540
This isn't a situation
you can fix with money.

356
00:22:11,870 --> 00:22:14,540
If money can't fix it,
I'll have to find another way.

357
00:22:16,670 --> 00:22:18,580
I need you to go meet...

358
00:22:19,680 --> 00:22:21,180
with Baek Jin Ju.

359
00:22:26,320 --> 00:22:28,390
(Hanbit High School
62nd Graduation Ceremony)

360
00:22:28,450 --> 00:22:30,550
Dad, I've...

361
00:22:31,250 --> 00:22:34,320
reclaimed my name as Baek Jin Ju...

362
00:22:34,660 --> 00:22:36,190
and requested a reinvestigation.

363
00:22:37,290 --> 00:22:40,700
From now on,
I have to fight Park Tae Ho head-on.

364
00:22:42,530 --> 00:22:45,670
Help us win, Dad.

365
00:22:51,640 --> 00:22:53,380
(Incoming call)

366
00:22:56,650 --> 00:22:57,910
Yes, hello?

367
00:22:58,750 --> 00:22:59,950
Is this Baek Jin Ju?

368
00:23:00,420 --> 00:23:02,250
This is Deputy Chief Yun Hyeong Su
of the National Police Agency.

369
00:23:03,750 --> 00:23:05,590
What do you want with me?

370
00:23:05,960 --> 00:23:08,160
I hear you requested
a reinvestigation with the NPA.

371
00:23:08,460 --> 00:23:09,960
I'd like to meet with you about it.

372
00:23:10,990 --> 00:23:14,500
- Why you?
- Because I'm debating...

373
00:23:15,530 --> 00:23:18,340
whether to help you
or ruin your chances...

374
00:23:18,340 --> 00:23:19,340
with the reinvestigation.

375
00:23:21,040 --> 00:23:23,810
So Park Tae Ho told you
to obstruct me?

376
00:23:24,710 --> 00:23:27,440
He did give his orders,
but I'm ignoring them.

377
00:23:28,150 --> 00:23:29,610
I'd rather make a deal with you.

378
00:23:30,510 --> 00:23:31,650
What if I offer you Park Cheol Su?

379
00:23:32,680 --> 00:23:34,850
What? Park Cheol Su?

380
00:23:35,450 --> 00:23:38,160
If you're interested, come meet me.
I'll send you the time and place.

381
00:23:44,560 --> 00:23:46,800
(On Seodam, 111-2 Soseomun-ro 3-gil,
Jung-gu, Seoul, 11 a.m.)

382
00:23:53,140 --> 00:23:54,140
Jin Ju.

383
00:23:55,510 --> 00:23:56,510
What's wrong?

384
00:23:58,710 --> 00:24:03,050
Deputy Chief Yun wants to meet.
He says he has a deal for me.

385
00:24:03,050 --> 00:24:04,110
What?

386
00:24:05,450 --> 00:24:08,320
Wait, isn't this another one
of Park Tae Ho's schemes?

387
00:24:09,390 --> 00:24:11,590
Rather than that,
I think he's weighing his options...

388
00:24:12,090 --> 00:24:13,920
between Park Tae Ho and me.

389
00:24:14,620 --> 00:24:16,560
He offered up Park Cheol Su,

390
00:24:16,960 --> 00:24:19,300
saying he could either help
or ruin the reinvestigation.

391
00:24:19,830 --> 00:24:22,970
I should at least meet him first
and see if a deal is possible.

392
00:24:23,870 --> 00:24:25,940
No way. That's too dangerous.

393
00:24:26,440 --> 00:24:29,010
If I avoid him and he ends up
sabotaging the reinvestigation,

394
00:24:29,010 --> 00:24:30,110
we'll be in serious trouble.

395
00:24:31,040 --> 00:24:33,210
Besides, the meeting place is just
a regular tea house.

396
00:24:34,810 --> 00:24:35,850
I'll be fine.

397
00:24:38,480 --> 00:24:40,750
Fine. Then I'm going with you,
all right?

398
00:24:41,080 --> 00:24:42,090
Okay.

399
00:24:51,760 --> 00:24:53,230
(Park Tae Ho)

400
00:24:54,430 --> 00:24:55,500
Mrs. Ok.

401
00:24:56,630 --> 00:24:59,070
What brings you here at this hour?

402
00:25:00,540 --> 00:25:02,270
There's something I need to ask you.

403
00:25:02,840 --> 00:25:06,580
It's about Chloe, I mean,
Baek Jin Ju, isn't it?

404
00:25:06,940 --> 00:25:09,150
So you already knew.

405
00:25:09,810 --> 00:25:12,820
It caused a huge commotion
in the house.

406
00:25:13,480 --> 00:25:14,480
I see.

407
00:25:14,850 --> 00:25:17,820
I don't think Park Tae Ho
will leave Jin Ju alone.

408
00:25:18,790 --> 00:25:22,230
If he's planning anything,
could you let me know?

409
00:25:22,990 --> 00:25:26,200
Please be sure to contact
Min Jun or me.

410
00:25:26,560 --> 00:25:27,560
I will.

411
00:25:28,800 --> 00:25:29,800
Thank you.

412
00:25:30,600 --> 00:25:32,000
You're always helping me.

413
00:25:32,400 --> 00:25:34,140
Even on the day
of the emergency board meeting,

414
00:25:34,540 --> 00:25:36,370
you knew in advance and helped me.

415
00:25:36,810 --> 00:25:39,380
I should get back inside.

416
00:25:39,740 --> 00:25:43,050
I'll keep a close eye on things
related to Ms. Baek,

417
00:25:43,210 --> 00:25:44,210
so don't you worry.

418
00:25:52,220 --> 00:25:54,620
Is she trying to avoid
talking about herself?

419
00:25:56,430 --> 00:26:00,560
In any case, she'll help make sure
nothing happens to Jin Ju, right?

420
00:26:05,140 --> 00:26:06,540
Yes, I'm here.

421
00:26:07,170 --> 00:26:09,310
- Aren't you here yet?
- I'm in the parking lot.

422
00:26:09,570 --> 00:26:11,070
I'll be right there, so just...

423
00:26:12,380 --> 00:26:13,540
Are you okay?

424
00:26:14,840 --> 00:26:15,850
Are you kidding me?

425
00:26:16,680 --> 00:26:17,910
Yes, I'm fine.

426
00:26:18,820 --> 00:26:20,450
Someone just hit my parked car.

427
00:26:21,250 --> 00:26:22,720
It's nothing serious.

428
00:26:23,390 --> 00:26:24,720
I'll sort this out quickly
and be right up.

429
00:26:25,490 --> 00:26:27,290
- Got it.
- Sure.

430
00:26:29,430 --> 00:26:30,530
Ms. Baek Jin Ju?

431
00:26:44,940 --> 00:26:45,940
Gosh, that's hot.

432
00:26:47,540 --> 00:26:51,150
Is this what they call
fighting heat with heat?

433
00:26:51,610 --> 00:26:54,320
Drinking this when it's hot out
is really good for you.

434
00:26:54,450 --> 00:26:55,490
Go ahead, try some.

435
00:26:55,950 --> 00:26:58,960
What do you mean you want
to make a deal with me?

436
00:26:59,760 --> 00:27:01,990
If I give you more money
than Park Tae Ho promised,

437
00:27:02,230 --> 00:27:03,590
are you saying you'll help us?

438
00:27:04,060 --> 00:27:06,400
Come on, what's the rush?

439
00:27:06,800 --> 00:27:08,970
The tea's getting cold,
so drink up first.

440
00:27:09,470 --> 00:27:10,530
Let's take our time talking.

441
00:27:16,510 --> 00:27:19,980
Offering up Park Cheol Su means
you know exactly where he is.

442
00:27:20,280 --> 00:27:23,250
I'm the one who got him out
and hid him,

443
00:27:24,080 --> 00:27:25,280
so of course I know.

444
00:27:25,550 --> 00:27:28,180
Where is Park Cheol Su right now?

445
00:27:29,650 --> 00:27:30,820
Be patient.

446
00:27:31,450 --> 00:27:33,290
The tea won't taste good
if it gets cold.

447
00:27:44,230 --> 00:27:45,940
I just have to make a quick call.

448
00:27:55,610 --> 00:27:57,780
You're monitoring
Park Cheol Su closely, right?

449
00:27:58,980 --> 00:28:00,080
What?

450
00:28:00,780 --> 00:28:02,790
He's meeting Chairman Park?

451
00:28:03,090 --> 00:28:04,090
At Adele of all places?

452
00:28:05,620 --> 00:28:07,760
Darn. Is he trying to smuggle him
out of the country...

453
00:28:07,760 --> 00:28:09,190
before the reinvestigation?

454
00:28:11,030 --> 00:28:13,660
The reinvestigation review committee
is tomorrow, right?

455
00:28:17,270 --> 00:28:18,330
Yes, okay.

456
00:28:23,770 --> 00:28:26,780
Something urgent came up.
I have to go.

457
00:28:27,180 --> 00:28:29,180
We'll discuss the deal
some other time.

458
00:28:31,010 --> 00:28:32,020
Ms. Baek?

459
00:28:33,020 --> 00:28:34,320
Ms. Baek...

460
00:28:35,390 --> 00:28:36,420
Wait.

461
00:29:06,120 --> 00:29:08,750
(Severe chestnut allergy)

462
00:29:08,820 --> 00:29:10,490
(On Seodam, 111-2 Soseomun-ro 3-gil,
Jung-gu, Seoul)

463
00:29:17,430 --> 00:29:18,460
Yes, it's me.

464
00:29:19,600 --> 00:29:22,600
Ms. Baek has a chestnut allergy,
doesn't she?

465
00:29:24,770 --> 00:29:28,200
I think Chairman Park Tae Ho
is planning to use that against her.

466
00:29:28,740 --> 00:29:31,010
You have to find Ms. Baek quickly.

467
00:29:38,520 --> 00:29:40,750
I need to get to Adele
and secure Park Cheol Su.

468
00:29:42,050 --> 00:29:43,650
Is he still in the parking lot?

469
00:29:49,460 --> 00:29:51,160
My gosh, I'm so sorry.

470
00:29:53,200 --> 00:29:55,700
- Are you all right?
- Yes, thank you. I'm fine.

471
00:29:56,670 --> 00:29:58,600
- I'm sorry.
- It's all right.

472
00:30:13,080 --> 00:30:17,020
(Elevator Under Maintenance)

473
00:30:25,800 --> 00:30:28,800
(Elevator Under Maintenance,
Please Use the Stairs.)

474
00:30:38,610 --> 00:30:39,710
(Under Maintenance)

475
00:30:59,260 --> 00:31:00,260
My...

476
00:31:01,130 --> 00:31:02,270
My allergy medication is gone.

477
00:31:04,930 --> 00:31:06,200
Don't tell me Park Tae Ho...

478
00:31:20,350 --> 00:31:22,490
(Under Maintenance)

479
00:31:22,590 --> 00:31:24,220
(Park Min Jun)

480
00:31:47,910 --> 00:31:50,850
Perhaps it's the chestnuts
that were added,

481
00:31:52,920 --> 00:31:55,150
but this barley tea
tastes excellent.

482
00:32:45,230 --> 00:32:48,170
(Pearl in Red)

483
00:32:48,240 --> 00:32:49,240
Park Tae Ho!

484
00:32:49,740 --> 00:32:52,640
What did you do?
How could you hurt Jin Ju again?

485
00:32:53,240 --> 00:32:55,880
I still hold Park Hyun Jun's secret.

486
00:32:56,310 --> 00:32:58,280
If Chairman Park threatens me over
what happened with Baek Jin Ju,

487
00:32:58,780 --> 00:33:01,250
I'll just use Oh Jung Ran
and Park Hyun Jun to stop him.

488
00:33:01,350 --> 00:33:04,420
- I'm done relying on other people.
- Hyun Jun.

489
00:33:04,650 --> 00:33:05,820
You said it was all over.

490
00:33:05,820 --> 00:33:09,260
It's over! I'm telling you,
it's completely over!

491
00:33:10,960 --> 00:33:12,930
(Subtitles are provided by KOCOWA.)
